"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/860698","Department of Health and Social Care","false","2018-03-15","<p>The Department continues to work with the Money and Mental Health Policy Institute and a range of stakeholders from the financial and debt advice sectors and the British Medical Association to undertake the review, which we will publish in due course.</p>","Thurrock","Jackie Doyle-Price",,"2018-03-15T17:30:23.467Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/860698/answer","Biography information for Jackie Doyle-Price","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/860698/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/860698/answer",,,,,"17","Health and Social Care","Health and Social Care","2018-03-12","Mental Illness: Debts","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health and Social Care, pursuant to the Answer of 1 March 2018 to Question 130615, when the review of the effect of debt and financial difficulties on people with mental health problems will be (a) completed and (b) published.","false","Biography information for Catherine McKinnell","Newcastle upon Tyne North","Catherine McKinnell","132055"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/860699","Department of Health and Social Care","false","2018-03-15","<p>NHS England is finalising its Children and Young People’s Mental Health Tier 4 Service Review. There are currently no plans to publish a report.</p>","Thurrock","Jackie Doyle-Price",,"2018-03-15T17:33:19.183Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/860699/answer","Biography information for Jackie Doyle-Price","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/860699/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/860699/answer",,,,,"17","Health and Social Care","Health and Social Care","2018-03-12","Mental Health Services: Children and Young People","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health and Social Care, pursuant to the Answer of 26 February 2018 to Question 129636 when the National Service Review of all Children and Young People’s Mental Health Tier 4 services will be (a) completed and (b) published.","false","Biography information for Catherine McKinnell","Newcastle upon Tyne North","Catherine McKinnell","132056"
